These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, cherry, eggplant
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, chef
1. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
2. the fisherman is on the left or right of the chef##3
3. the fisherman is the person eating cherry##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
5. the paramedic is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | eggplant | lettuce | cherry |
| Job    | paramedic    | chef | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, puzzles, cooking
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, car
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | puzzles | cooking | writing |
| Transport   | car    | airplane     | snowmobile        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess, dancing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, reggae
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | dancing     | chess | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | disco     | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, western, comedy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, handball, baseball
1. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | western  | thriller  |
| Sport         | volleyball  | handball | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, baking, magic-tricks
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, french, egyptian
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the japanese##2
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
3. the egyptian is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | skydiving   | magic-tricks | baking    |
| Nationality   | french | egyptian     | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, reading, traveling
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, skiing, biathlon
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | reading | traveling | drawing   |
| Sport   | biathlon     | surfing    | skiing |

