.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, mystery
3 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, rabbit
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation | scientific |
| Pet           | horse         | ferret         | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, peas, grapefruit
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, mouse
1. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the person eating corn##2
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | peas | grapefruit | corn |
| Pet    | goldfish    | dog | mouse     |

