.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, techno, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, surfing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the fan of techno##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | techno  | reggae  |
| Sport         | rugby | surfing | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, sprite
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, banana, nectarine
1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4
3. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | sprite      | iced-tea |
| Food       | banana | nectarine | asparagus   |

