.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, engineer, electrician
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, motorbike, snowmobile
1. the electrician is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the person driving the van is the paramedic##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the electrician##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | engineer | electrician | paramedic |
| Transport   | motorbike | snowmobile   | van |

