.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, woodworking, fishing
3 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla, ferret
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the owner of the chinchilla##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | fishing | magic-tricks |
| Pet     | rat    | ferret  | chinchilla   |

