.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, adventure, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, rock, metal
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
4. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | zombie     | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | rock | house | metal    |

