.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, frog, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, weightlifting, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | frog  | rat   | snake |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | weightlifting | cycling       |

 